comments: Looney (GSW) and Suggs (ORL) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Banchero (ORL) turns to roll and incidental contact occurs with Wiggins (GSW) as Wiggins goes under the pick.
Wagner (ORL) rests his hands on Wiggins (GSW) as he goes to set the pick and the contact is marginal.
Wiggins (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position near Suggs (ORL) and marginal foot contact occurs as Suggs goes around the screen.

Replay review of the foul called on Wagner (ORL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Wagner is drawn into the air and initiates body contact with Curry (GSW) that affects his jump shot attempt.  Curry does not overtly or abruptly veer into the defender or launch at the defender to create the contact.
Looney (GSW) moves alongside Wagner's (ORL) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Curry (GSW) initiates contact with Suggs (ORL) that affects his ability to control the loose ball.
Green (GSW) brings his hands toward Wagner (ORL) and marginal contact occurs as Green (GSW) releases away to roll.
Wiggins (GSW) establishes himself in Suggs's (ORL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Wiggins (GSW) avoids dislodging Suggs (ORL) from his defensive position and marginal contact occurs as the two players come together.
Banchero (ORL) establishes himself in Thompson's (GSW) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Wiggins (GSW) establishes himself in Suggs' (ORL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Green (GSW) initiates contact with Suggs (ORL) that affects his SQBR after the steal.
Curry (GSW) establishes himself in Suggs's (ORL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.

comments: Banchero (ORL) throws the ball out of bounds.
Okeke (ORL) maintains a legal guarding position and incidental contact occurs as he defends Curry (GSW).

Carter Jr. (ORL) rests and removes his hand from Thompson's (GSW) body and does not deliver force during Thompson's shot attempt.
